                <summary>On Oct. 31st, at the Union Hotel in Greencastle, Rev. J. Rebaugh married
                    William Wolford to Susannah Cunningham, of Washington co., Md. On Nov. 1st, at
                    the bride's father's home, Rev. J. Rebaugh married William Valentine, of
                    Washington co., Md., to Elizabeth Smith, of Franklin co. On Nov. 8th, in
                    Greencastle, Rev. J. Rebaugh married Henry T. Creps to Catharine Switzer, all of
                    Washington Twp., Franklin co. On Nov. 15th, at the home of the bride's father,
                    Henry Blays married Sophia G. Sharpless, both of Washington co., Md. On Oct.
                    11th, Rev. H. Hummelbaugh married Levi Crider to Elizabeth Johns, all of
                    Letterkenny Twp., Franklin co. On Nov. 20th, at the bride's father's home, Rev.
                    J. Smith Gordon married Lieutenant S. O. McCurdy to Bell Witherow, daughter of
                    John Witherow, Esq., all of Fannetsburg.</summary>
