                    died of apoplexy at age 81. On Nov. 19th, in Greencastle, Simon Rupley, Sr.,
                    died at age 67. On Nov. 20th, in Hamilton Twp., John Miller died of apoplexy at
                    age 61. On Nov. 11th, at his home in Amberson's Valley, in Franklin co., Daniel
                    Struble died at age 78. On Nov. 11th, an his home in Guilford Twp., Elias
                    Fetterhoof Oyler died of a lingering illness at age 32.</summary>
